{"type":"message","id":"67185af0","parentId":"8794d800","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:03:51.616Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/focus is not a recognized command. Here's what I can help with:\n\n**Session controls:**\n- `/reasoning` — toggle thinking mode on/off\n- `/status` or `📊` — show session status card\n\n**Available skills** (read with `read <path>`):\n- `gortex-guide` — code intelligence tools\n- `gortex-explore` — explore unfamiliar code\n- `gortex-debug` — trace errors\n- `gortex-impact` — safety analysis before changes\n- `gortex-refactor` — rename, extract, restructure\n- `diagram-maker` — create diagrams\n- `spike` — feasibility prototypes\n- `taskflow` — durable multi-step jobs\n- And more — see full list in context\n\n**What do you want to do?**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":32030,"output":168,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32710,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779271422459,"responseId":"msg_g9uqKXRmt922eIJWb7Nn7dcI"}}
