{"type":"message","id":"f0ecb062","parentId":"f3d0942a","timestamp":"2026-05-20T10:18:29.387Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Fixed 2 bugs in `udd-web/lib/ai/service.ts`:\n\n**Bug 1** — `persistFiles` (line 357)\n- **Was:** `if (!result.files.length) return;`\n- **Now:** `if (!result.files?.length) return;`\n- **Crash:** `TypeError: Cannot read properties of undefined (reading 'length')` if generator returns no `files` property\n\n**Bug 2** — `runAITask` \"completed\" event (line 313)\n- **Was:** `file_count: result.files.length,`\n- **Now:** `file_count: result.files?.length ?? 0,`\n- **Crash:** Same pattern — crashes if `result.files` is undefined during the completion event write\n\nBoth are the same root cause: assuming `result.files` is always present on `AITaskResult`. The generator could return an error result or malformed response without a `files` array, and either crash would leave the task in an inconsistent state instead of failing gracefully."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"kimi","model":"kimi-for-coding","usage":{"input":445,"output":214,"cacheRead":54016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54675,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779272298810,"responseId":"msg_TAIGPRyWBckfMfIVkBI7JIXG"}}
